content:
Great Claude! Glad to have you onboard as CTO! We are stuck on transcript_processor (in Project knowledge) file errors. The last chat identified many indentation errors in the previous file, so rebuilt it, not from a functionality standpoint, but to just clean up the file. I restarted the server and ran the test. Below are the results. We have been working on this for many chats now. How do we get this fixed?

python3 test_system.py
